Jeff Green is 37 years old.

Jeff Green was born on August 28, 1986.

Jeff Green is 6-8 (203 cm) tall.

How much does Jeff Green weigh?

Jeff Green weighs 235 lbs (106 kg).

Jeff Green is not in the Hall of Fame.

Jeff Green was drafted by Boston Celtics, 1st round (5th pick, 5th overall), 2007 NBA Draft.

Power Forward, Small Forward, and Center.

Jeff Green averages 6.5 points, 2.3 rebounds, and 0.9 assists per game.
